    list_wells = ['DIJAR-3','DIJAR-4','DIJAR-8','DIJAR-1-1']
initial_time = np.arange(len(list_wells))
capex = [-212000,-276000,-385000,-212000]
list_wells_sched=[]

prod_eagle = prob_prod.get_sample(1000)
price_eagle = prob_oil_price.get_sample(1000)   

for i, well in enumerate(list_wells):

    p = Period(
        name='base',
        dca = dca.Arps(
        qi = prod_eagle.tolist(),
        di = 0.005102753514909305/5,
        freq_di='D',
        ti = initial_time[i],
        b=1,
        ),
        start = 0,
        end=36,
        freq_output='M',
        freq_input='M',
        cashflow_params = [
        {
            'name':'wo',
            'value':capex[i],
            'periods':1,
            'target':'capex'
        },
        {
            'name':'Opex',
            'value':-7,
            'multiply': 'oil_volume',
            'target':'opex'
        },
        {
            'name':'Income',
            'value':price_eagle.tolist(),
            'multiply': 'oil_volume',
            'target':'income',
            'wi':0.92
        },
        {
            'name':'abandon',
            'value':-200000,
            'periods':-1,
            'target':'capex'
        },

        ]
    )
    s = Scenario(name='sc', periods = [p])
    w = Well(
        name = list_wells[i],
        scenarios = [
            s
        ]
    )
    list_wells_sched.append(w)

eagle_wells = WellsGroup(name='eagle',wells=list_wells_sched)
eagle_wells.tree()
    list_wells = ['DIJAR-3','DIJAR-4','DIJAR-8','DIJAR-1-1'] initial_time = np.arange(len(list_wells)) capex = [-212000,-276000,-385000,-212000] list_wells_sched=[] prod_eagle = prob_prod.get_sample(1000) price_eagle = prob_oil_price.get_sample(1000) for i, well in enumerate(list_wells): p = Period( name='base', dca = dca.Arps( qi = prod_eagle.tolist(), di = 0.005102753514909305/5, freq_di='D', ti = initial_time[i], b=1, ), start = 0, end=36, freq_output='M', freq_input='M', cashflow_params = [ { 'name':'wo', 'value':capex[i], 'periods':1, 'target':'capex' }, { 'name':'Opex', 'value':-7, 'multiply': 'oil_volume', 'target':'opex' }, { 'name':'Income', 'value':price_eagle.tolist(), 'multiply': 'oil_volume', 'target':'income', 'wi':0.92 }, { 'name':'abandon', 'value':-200000, 'periods':-1, 'target':'capex' }, ] ) s = Scenario(name='sc', periods = [p]) w = Well( name = list_wells[i], scenarios = [ s ] ) list_wells_sched.append(w) eagle_wells = WellsGroup(name='eagle',wells=list_wells_sched) eagle_wells.tree()
